    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "pipeline_detail",
      "x": 70, "y": 452,
      "width": 340, "height": 252,
      "text": "class MessagePipeline:\n  switchboard_pool: asyncpg.Pool\n  dispatch_fn: spawner.trigger\n  source_butler: \"switchboard\"\n  enable_ingress_dedupe: true\n  enable_identity_resolution: bool\n  notify_owner_fn: Callable\n\nConcurrent session handling:\n  max_concurrent_sessions: 3\n  ContextVar per asyncio task\n  → cross-task isolation\n\nClassification categories:\n  finance  ·  travel  ·  health\n  relationship  ·  general (fallback)\n  finance vs travel: intent-based tie-break\n\nConversation history strategies:\n  telegram / whatsapp → realtime\n    (last 15min OR last 30 msgs)\n  email → full chain (50k tokens)\n  api / mcp → none\n\nRouting decision:\n  LLM calls route_to_butler tool\n  fallback: text inference (single match)\n  ambiguous → route to general butler",
      "originalText": "class MessagePipeline:\n  switchboard_pool: asyncpg.Pool\n  dispatch_fn: spawner.trigger\n  source_butler: \"switchboard\"\n  enable_ingress_dedupe: true\n  enable_identity_resolution: bool\n  notify_owner_fn: Callable\n\nConcurrent session handling:\n  max_concurrent_sessions: 3\n  ContextVar per asyncio task\n  → cross-task isolation\n\nClassification categories:\n  finance  ·  travel  ·  health\n  relationship  ·  general (fallback)\n  finance vs travel: intent-based tie-break\n\nConversation history strategies:\n  telegram / whatsapp → realtime\n    (last 15min OR last 30 msgs)\n  email → full chain (50k tokens)\n  api / mcp → none\n\nRouting decision:\n  LLM calls route_to_butler tool\n  fallback: text inference (single match)\n  ambiguous → route to general butler",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
