      "text": "Three asyncio.Queue tiers:\n  high_priority  (capacity 100)\n  interactive       (capacity 100)\n  default            (capacity 100)\n\nStarvation guard:\n  max_consecutive_same_tier: 10\n  forced lower-tier dequeue",
      "originalText": "Three asyncio.Queue tiers:\n  high_priority  (capacity 100)\n  interactive       (capacity 100)\n  default            (capacity 100)\n\nStarvation guard:\n  max_consecutive_same_tier: 10\n  forced lower-tier dequeue",
