      "id": "buffer_backpressure",
      "x": 445, "y": 578,
      "width": 460, "height": 30,
      "text": "Backpressure: when all tier queues full → hot path skips enqueue (message already in DB)\n→ scanner recovers on next sweep  ·  worker_count: 3",
