    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "identity_detail",
      "x": 70, "y": 764,
      "width": 350, "height": 124,
      "text": "shared.contacts\n  id, roles[] (e.g. ['owner']), entity_id → memory\n  one canonical row per known person/actor\n\nshared.contact_info\n  type + value UNIQUE  (e.g. telegram:chat_id)\n  secured=true → credential entries\n  FK → shared.contacts.id\n\nIngress reverse-lookup: (type, value) → contact_id\nIdentity preamble injected into LLM routing prompt\nBootstrapped automatically on daemon startup (owner)",
      "originalText": "shared.contacts\n  id, roles[] (e.g. ['owner']), entity_id → memory\n  one canonical row per known person/actor\n\nshared.contact_info\n  type + value UNIQUE  (e.g. telegram:chat_id)\n  secured=true → credential entries\n  FK → shared.contacts.id\n\nIngress reverse-lookup: (type, value) → contact_id\nIdentity preamble injected into LLM routing prompt\nBootstrapped automatically on daemon startup (owner)",
